+- **Circular dependency risk**: `global/index.ts` exempt from migration (confirmed)
+- **External SDK compatibility**: `Env.set()` must sync to `process.env` (confirmed)
+- **Migration atomicity**: All files in single commit to avoid inconsistency
+- **Exclusion documentation**: Add comments explaining WHY exemptions exist
